Heat oil in large saucepan on medium heat. Add onions; cook 5 minutes or until tender, stirring frequently. Add broccoli, potatoes, broth, water and pepper; stir. Bring to boil; simmer on medium-low heat 15 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Add soup to blender in batches; blend until smooth. Return to pan. Whisk in Cooking Creme; cook and stir 2 to 3 minutes or until heated through.